<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>daya śālivāhana śa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kavarṣaṁbbulu 1678 A 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>guneṭi yuvanāma saṁvva 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>tsara vaiśākha ba 5 budha 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vāraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> viciriśeṭla gō 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>trōdbhavuḍaina mailavara 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>pu basuvanna komāruḍu 
<lb n="9"/>malliśeṭṭi tōvviṁccina bhāvi 
<lb n="10"/>śivālayaṁ hanumaṁ 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ttuni midde yī śubha 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>dinamaṁddu kūpa saṁni 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dhānamaṁddu malleśvarā 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>rppitaṁgā cēśina pratiṣṭha <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

